data.description:
Location is prime at this 3 bed/3 bath end unit townhouse near Bass Lake Road/Maple Grove Parkway and near Waver Lake,  and many walking/biking trails.
All bedrooms upstairs with a loft and laundry. Private owner's suite with vaulted ceiling, walk-in closet, private bath and double sink vanity. 
Lots of natural lights, cherry millwork and cabinets. Fire sprinkler system throughout.
Main level kitchen with granite counters, stainless-steel appliances, breakfast bar, and bayed dining
Gas fireplace in living room, tall ceilings, and comfortable setting. 
Motivated Seller, bring an offer!!
